Package: LinRegTrunc
Type: Package
Title: Fit Linear Models With Truncated Normally Distributed Errors
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mathieu", "Fortin", email = "mathieu.fortin.re@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6436-2727")),
    person("His Majesty the King in right of Canada", role=c("cph")))
Description: Fit linear models whose residual error distribution can be 
    truncated due to natural constraints. This is likely to happen with
    allometric relationships and growth modelling data, even though the
    response variable is transformed. 
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: 
    J4R (>= 1.2.1)
